"title": "8404: commands, in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8404: commands, in ot",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The OT sets out the commands of God to his people Israel, indicating both their extent and their importance.</p>\n<h2>The reason for God's commands: the need to be holy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:7-Lev20:8\">LEV 20:7–20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:26\">LEV 20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:8\">LEV 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's commands to Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:31-Deut5:33\">DEU 5:31–5:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:23-Exod16:24\">EXO 16:23–16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:1\">EXO 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:22\">EXO 25:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:32\">EXO 34:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:18-Num9:20\">NUM 9:18–9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:11\">DEU 15:11</a> <em>The LORD commands generosity and kindness to the poor</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:15\">DEU 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17-Deut24:18\">DEU 24:17–24:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:21-Deut24:22\">DEU 24:21–24:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:25-2Chr29:26\">2CH 29:25–29:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:1\">NEH 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:13-Neh9:14\">NEH 9:13–9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Demands made by God upon individuals</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a> <em>Adam</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:16\">GEN 7:16</a> <em>Noah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:4\">GEN 21:4</a> <em>Abraham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:9\">LEV 6:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:38\">NUM 33:38</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:13\">NUM 24:13</a> <em>Baalam</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:23\">DEU 31:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:16-Josh4:17\">JOS 4:16–4:17</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:25</a> <em>King David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:14</a> <em>King Solomon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36\">1KI 18:36</a> <em>Elijah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:7\">JER 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:2\">JER 26:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:9-Ezek37:10\">EZK 37:9–37:10</a> <em>Ezekiel</em></p>\n<h2>God's commands to non-human agencies</h2>\n<h3>The universe</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:6-Ps33:9\">PSA 33:6–33:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:4-Ps148:6\">PSA 148:4–148:6</a></p>\n<h3>The living creation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:13\">2CH 7:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:27\">JOB 39:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:3\">AMO 9:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:10\">JON 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>The non-living creation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:11-Job37:12\">JOB 37:11–37:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:23-Ps78:24\">PSA 78:23–78:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:6\">ISA 5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:35\">JER 31:35</a></p>\n<h3>The angels</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11\">PSA 91:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:20\">PSA 103:20</a></p>\n<h3>The sword, symbolising the judgment of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer47:6-Jer47:7\">JER 47:6–47:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:4\">AMO 9:4</a></p>\n<h2>Commands of the leaders of God's people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:24-Deut31:26\">DEU 31:24–31:26</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:16-Josh1:18\">JOS 1:16–1:18</a> <em>Joshua</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:40\">1KI 18:40</a> <em>Elijah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:22\">NEH 13:22</a> <em>Nehemiah</em></p>\n<h2>Commands given by kings</h2>\n<h3>Over Israel and Judah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:46\">1KI 2:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:20-1Chr28:21\">1CH 28:20–28:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:4\">2CH 14:4</a></p>\n<h3>Over heathen nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:20\">GEN 12:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:22\">EXO 1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:3\">EZR 4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:12\">EST 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:15\">EST 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:8\">EST 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:2\">EST 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:13\">EST 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:20-Dan3:22\">DAN 3:20–3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:29\">DAN 5:29</a></p>\n<h2>Parental commands</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:44-Deut32:46\">DEU 32:44–32:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:1\">PRO 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20\">PRO 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:1-Prov7:2\">PRO 7:1–7:2</a></p>\n<h2>The nature of God's commands</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:10\">PSA 19:7–19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:15\">1CH 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:86\">PSA 119:86</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:96\">PSA 119:96</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:151\">PSA 119:151</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:172\">PSA 119:172</a></p>\n<h2>God's commands are to be loved</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:47-Ps119:48\">PSA 119:47–119:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:61\">1KI 8:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:19\">1CH 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:12\">JOB 23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1\">PSA 112:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:16\">PSA 119:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:35\">PSA 119:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:127-Ps119:128\">PSA 119:127–119:128</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:131\">PSA 119:131</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:143\">PSA 119:143</a></p>\n<h2>God's commands are to be obeyed</h2>\n<h3>God commands obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">ECC 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:2\">DEU 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16-Deut26:18\">DEU 26:16–26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:22-Jer7:23\">JER 7:22–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Warnings against and examples of disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:14\">2KI 17:13–17:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13-1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:13–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:10-1Kgs11:11\">1KI 11:10–11:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:18\">LAM 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:6\">DAN 9:4–9:6</a></p>\n<h3>The consequences of obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:3\">DEU 6:1–6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:4-Gen26:5\">GEN 26:4–26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:26\">EXO 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:1\">DEU 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:1\">DEU 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">1KI 11:38</a></p>\n<h3>The consequences of disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:14-1Sam12:15\">1SA 12:14–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:26-Deut11:28\">DEU 11:26–11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:1-Deut30:3\">DEU 30:1–30:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:4-1Kgs9:9\">1KI 9:4–9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:7-Neh1:9\">NEH 1:7–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:4-Jer22:5\">JER 22:4–22:5</a></p>",
